name: Ciclo // Cycle
description: What if the cycle of day did not exist?  We would only see the coldness of the night or the burning of the day What do we become when we get stuck in the routine?  In a bland atmosphere, without sunrises or sunsets. Change colors, leave everyone amazed with the beauty of your skies. // 2020 // 4000 x 6000 px // 300 dpi
